channel.title: Magnum-Scape (Last Update 9-5-09) Base-Devo [Mainly pics atm]
channel.description:
[b]Videos:[/b] Prayer Switching: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h_I8_hJobyg Vengence, and Fishing Arena: http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=ndwnjb&s=3 Bank Video: http://tinypic.com/usermedia.php?uo=bXcZ8D...kQbW4h4l5k2TGxc Emote Interface: http://tinypic.com/player.php?v=23tzbk&s=3 Magic Interfaces: http://tinypic.com/m/5a4bi1/3
[b]Pictures:[/b] [img]http://i31.tinypic.com/dlkspx.png[/img] [img]http://i30.tinypic.com/2yyecmw.jpg[/img] [img]http://i28.tinypic.com/2zrpcug.jpg[/img] [img]http://i25.tinypic.com/242fw9k.jpg[/img] [img]http://i29.tinypic.com/17en41.jpg[/img] Updates: ItemMethod Complete, which means MORE CUSTOMS GUYS! 100% Woodcutting. [img]http://i26.tinypic.com/28t8dtz.png[/img] Prayer Interface Complete, exactly Like runescape.
Server should be out in a week or two, Almost near completion (Has a PK server up right now) Features:
[ul][*]Magnum Portal Updated, more functional for users. [*]New Report System, exactly Like runescape, will be integrated with Forums and Server. [*]100% Prayer in game, Prayer switching is complete (Click protect from Range, then click Smite, Range Headicon will be replaced with Smite) See Image, [url=http://"http://www.magnum-scape.com/upload/server/3v12.png"][b]Prayer Swiching[/b][/url] [*]New Genie Random Event, will come from nowhere, give lamp, and disappear. [*]Using Events to Run Processes instead of Process Boolean. [*]Working on New combat, will use Devolution 2.4 as base. [*]100% InGame and Forum Highscores, has option to choose between Pk Kills and Highscores [*]New Npc and PVP minigame, Each pvp kill you get 1 point, then every 100 Npcs you kill you get 1 point. This will be used for special items. [*]New customs See this image; [url=http://"http://www.magnum-scape.com/upload/server/v31.png"][b]Custom Items[/b][/url] [*]100% Dueling, Staking, Select Armour you want to NOT be worn, ect. Here's an Image; [b][url=http://"http://www.magnum-scape.com/upload/server/v312.png"]Full Dueling[/url][/b] [*]Multi wilderness Icon loading correctly. [*]Wilderness Icon loading Correctly. [*]Wilderness Level icon loading Correctly [*]Inferno Adze 80% Burns more logs as level progresses [*]Added new Runescape prayers, Ill add a pic tonight [*]Clan chat 80%, Clan Setup almost complete. [*]Started Pest Control, will Finish Later. (8-18-09) Pest Control Complete! [*]Castle Wars Started, Will finish Later.[/ul]
[size=9pt]Server/Client Coder: Demetri .. Server Coder: Jay[/size]
And so many more! Comments? Negative, and I'll rape you, cause this is just too sexy ;) I know we can't advertise, but if you're looking for the link just PM me [size=5pt]or look in my siggy :D[/size]
